title: Dichotomyctere
text:
Dichotomyctere is a <a href="genus">genus</a> of relatively small <a href="pufferfish">pufferfish</a> found in both fresh and <a href="brackish">brackish</a> waters in <a href="South%20Asia">south</a> and <a href="southeast%20Asia">southeast Asia</a>. Its species were generally included in the genus "<a href="Tetraodon">Tetraodon</a>" until 2013. The largest species of "Dichotomyctere" reach up to in length.
